description.@value: 3回の調査の調査の概要、調査対象地域の各地の概要、地図の解説、および地図の各シートの根拠となった数値の総覧、三角測量の利点に関する議論を含む。

This volume includes an outline of Stein’s third expedition, with descriptions of all the sites he visited and explanations of the maps, including survey of the numerical values for each map and a discussion of the merits of triangulation.
